132
00:08:21,826 --> 00:08:22,826
Yes, yes, I'll draw.

133
00:08:30,761 --> 00:08:33,169
So, when did we first meet?

134
00:08:34,636 --> 00:08:36,135
That day, the award ceremony of

135
