222
00:13:38,385 --> 00:13:39,385
Forget it.

223
00:13:39,745 --> 00:13:40,905
He'll just bring the teacher

224
00:13:40,930 --> 00:13:42,050
here directly.

225
00:13:43,504 --> 00:13:44,504
