230
00:13:58,226 --> 00:13:59,827
I envy you, brother Xiao.

231
00:14:01,559 --> 00:14:02,668
You've already found

232
00:14:02,684 --> 00:14:03,855
what you want to do.

233
00:14:05,800 --> 00:14:06,929
