234
00:14:07,649 --> 00:14:09,023
Do what you love,

235
00:14:09,120 --> 00:14:10,120
and love who you want to love.

236
00:14:11,649 --> 00:14:13,565
Honestly, I didn't fully understand

237
00:14:13,937 --> 00:14:15,432
